## 8. Agent-Agnostic Context Injection Integration
* **File Target:** `server/src/features/on-demand-agents/context-builders/technical-issues.builder.ts`
* **Execution Logic:** When compiling prompts for the "Technical SEO and AI-readiness expert" agent, the feature context builder must pull from database records.
* **Constraint Limits:** Query and fetch the **latest 20 page results** from `llm_audit_results`.
* **Injection Context:** Pass these records directly into the agent context prompt layer, enabling the agent to analyze historical project metrics without invoking a new live web crawler cycle.